first step: 
 mkdir redux-demo
 npm init
 npm install redux
 touch index.js   code: console.log('From index.js')
 node index.js show: From index.js
 
 second step:
  Three Core Concepts
   
  Three Principles
   The state of your whole application is stored in an tree within a single store
   整个应用的 state 被储存在一棵 object tree 中，并且这个 object tree 只存在于唯一一个 store 中
   Second Principles
    The only way to change the state is to emit an action, an object describing what happing
    唯一改变 state 的方法就是触发 action，action 是一个用于描述已发生事件的普通对象
   Third Principles
    To specify how the state tree is transformed by action, you write pure reducers
    为了描述 action 如何改变 state tree ，你需要编写 reducers
   
   Three Principles Overview:
    Javascript App
    redux store(state)---->App----dispatch--->Action---->Reducer----->redux store(state)
    
   在node的解释器中是不能使用imort from 它要用 require代替才行
   Example: index.js
    ```
    import {createStore} from 'redux' no
    const redux = require('redux') yes
    const createStore = redux.createStore yes
    ```
    node index.js
   

   
    
  
  
   
